{"tid":1153651,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"falling","createTime":"2019-05-13T18:43:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T13:48:00.000Z","uid":238801,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"12fd7246312d64d16b5484d7d4286b1ec61d4b48","tid":1153651,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T18:43:19.000Z","msg":"好鍾意唔知點我 <br />\n但係搞到明明係又<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你明唔明真係好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但2種開心係佢要叫係咁 我都唔知 唔想返工所以唔想瞓<br />\n好想聽日又一日懶下懶下又一日 一放假就好想一直放假<br />\n好想一直可以咁開心刻係冇得做都好開心 係真係開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都唔明揀 我最<br />\n硬係覺得怕人有曬咪幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可以痴唔能夠並存<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要keep一定要<br />\n明明人 好想痴住佢 其實我唔係想專登 啲咩<br />\n因為我驚柒 <br />\n點解住佢本來全日但嗰好似唔諗 但明明自己相處落係舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後拖到一樣嘢都唔係好想做 拖下拖下撚憎做選擇 可以一個<br />\n利申狗公detector on<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2db8650e19ebab4ba57380df10ea7a9ad3b62e66","tid":1153651,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T18:44:34.000Z","msg":"重組句子式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好爽打撚曬出來但睇唔明"},{"pid":"c87d9de1dd32e5f5b5376c28d011e0f88eedbd52","tid":1153651,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T18:46:32.000Z","msg":"唔是我唔願瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />是尋晚太撚鬆懈 拖撚到9點先瞓 我今晚可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb2c47179348acefb62ae79f32a25edced904b11","tid":1153651,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T18:46:57.000Z","msg":"但呢兩日加埋真係幾開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b28fe05eacb74b25419bb1f42b92bea39db00afc","tid":1153651,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T18:49:26.000Z","msg":"佢一返嚟我真係勁開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係唔係好知姐 唉<br />\n如果唔係我都冇辦法 反正個人大咗 開始識唔顧人感受啲<br />\n正確線我都係會 但人大真係要愛自己多過一切 冇辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fa33b5c796955ab8546660a5f5a82471d767c93","tid":1153651,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T18:56:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d891e34689dfeb4ae7ea08138da048d652af2d07","tid":1153651,"uid":124256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T18:56:58.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"23c3fa46d09ec72a8b3489c6f5a38f4d2c385166","tid":1153651,"uid":124256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T18:57:18.000Z","msg":"一入嚟就見到你個垃圾名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e9b82886d0512d735b748e7d8d67193004db3cf","tid":1153651,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d891e34689dfeb4ae7ea08138da048d652af2d07","tid":1153651,"uid":124256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T18:56:58.000Z","msg":"係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T18:57:37.000Z","msg":"唔洗瞓？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"616bfb7fa39b666126a4c79aa3d46af879aec110","tid":1153651,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23c3fa46d09ec72a8b3489c6f5a38f4d2c385166","tid":1153651,"uid":124256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T18:57:18.000Z","msg":"一入嚟就見到你個垃圾名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" c